short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Keyboard shortcut to filter your current Google search results to only show pages created or modified in the past year.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Recently" is a Chrome Extension that creates a keyboard shortcut to limit your search results to the past year. Once Recently is installed, search Google as you normally would. When you want to limit your results to the past 12 months, press Shift + P to rerun your results with the "past year" filter applied.
